Váš priateľ, producent Gu Jak.

222
00:22:00,900 --> 00:22:02,900
Co-Producent.

223
00:22:02,900 --> 00:22:06,900
Sang Mi, Bok Ja, Joon Ik, Tae Hwan, Ho Young.

224
00:22:06,900 --> 00:22:12,900
